headline: Can Domino’s Shares Hit $550 in 2026?
summary: Domino’s Pizza (NYSE: DPZ) closed 2025 down 0.4% while peers like Yum! Brands surged 14%. That divergence has left DPZ trading near its 52-week low at $411, despite delivering some of the strongest profitability metrics in quick-service restaurants.
